Introduction

Min Jiwoon is a R&B singer and lyricist under KRUCIALIZE. She was a contestant on Vocal Play and made her solo debut under the name Min Ziwoon on June 15, 2018, with the digital single "Homerun". She made her re-debut on October 4, 2024, with the digital single "Sentimental Love".
